Back to Reality
---------------

I laid out the fundamental challenges driving the institution of the runtim=
e fee when it was announced last September ( https://stratechery.com/2023/u=
nitys-business-model-change-unitys-strategy-unity-leadership-questions/?acc=
ess_token=3DeyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6InN0cmF0ZWNoZXJ5LnBhc3Nwb3J0Lm9ubGl=
